Subject: drivers: remove get_task_comm() and print task comm directly
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 7e70433c2bf542e10c6e40084d8adb7325dc71cb
